	(429,10,'2015-09-30 08:00:17','2015-09-30 08:00:17','[vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]<strong>THE</strong> days when you had to wait for your favorite TV programs to slowly turn up on your pay-TV channels are numbered. So are the days when you have to tune in at a specific time to watch these programs.\n\nIndeed, with a plethora of online video services like Netflix, Amazon Instant Video and Hulu, TV is being viewed as and when viewers want. Instead of being restricted to the usual stable of programs, you get to choose from a lot more and at a time convenient to you. Plus, you can cut the cord\" and do without a pay-TV subscription.[/vc_column_text][vc_video title=\"A great ASUS YouTube Video\" link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yko99aL_UiI\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]As more cord-cutters are choosing to watch their favorite programs on the go, whether they are on the subway or in a cab, the choice of device is critical to ensure a great viewing experience.\n\nWhile there\'s a plethora of tablets to choose from, not every one is built to deliver all the eye candy that directors and visual effects artists had intended.\n\nThankfully, the innovative folks at Asus have placed display quality as one of their top priorities in designing the ZenPad, which was built from the ground-up to deliver a superb visual experience like no other.\n\nLet\'s start with Asus\' Tru2Life technology that powers the ZenPad. By using the latest image processing technology found on high-end TVs, the ZenPad is able to deliver incredibly realistic images with sharpness, detail and accurate contrast.\n\nWatching Christopher Nolan\'s Interstellar? You\'ll want the vast space in the movie to appear as black as it is, with stars lighting up like diamonds on a black blanket.\n\nThe ZenPad offers that, thanks to its intelligent contrast enhancement that provides wider dynamic range, giving you deep blacks and realistic images. Plus, with intelligent sharpness enhancement, the tablet will bring out even the smallest details in an image  like the stars in the night sky.\n\nEven if you\'re watching the movie on a clear day in a brightly-lit room, the ZenPad continues to deliver a clear and vivid experience. That\'s because the tablet sports an ambient sensor that adjusts the brightness and overall look of the display to fit different lighting conditions  without making images look washed out.\n\nMany cord-cutters often catch up on their favorite shows with their friends and loved ones. When doing so, you\'ll need a tablet with a wide viewing angle so the other viewers will not miss out on all the onscreen action.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Title\" title_align=\"separator_align_center\" align=\"align_center\" color=\"grey\" style=\"\" border_width=\"\" el_width=\"\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]Fans of Netflix\'s Daredevil will also be impressed with the ZenPad\'s ability to handle fast-moving scenes, like the epic fight between Charlie Cox\'s Daredevil and Peter Shinkoda\'s ninja assassin Nobu. The ZenPad increases the frame rate in such scenes, resulting in reduced blur and smooth, detailed motion.\n\nGreat visual effects are often accompanied by immersive audio tracks to keep viewers on the edge of their seats. However, the audio experience of most tablets is so lackluster that it\'s sometimes hard to make out the dialog and other sound effects in movies.\n\nFor a start, the ZenPad\'s dual speakers are positioned right in front of you  not at the sides or behind the screen. Not only do they sound three times louder than other devices, they also deliver DTS-HD Premium surround sound  the world\'s first tablet to do so.\n\nEven if you\'re not an audiophile, you\'ll be able to pick up the ZenPad\'s rich, detailed audio, whether you\'re listening through the tablet\'s speakers or your headphones. This crystal-clear, expansive audio experience was tuned by sound experts in the Asus Golden Ear team.\n\nFeel the need to turn up the volume and spruce up the sound effects at a house party? Cord-cutters will appreciate the Asus Audio Cover, the world\'s first 5.1-channel surround sound accessory that packs four satellite speakers, one center-channel speaker and a subwoofer! This takes cord-cutting to the next level, delivering a truly mobile movie experience on your own terms.\n\nIt\'s common for cord-cutters to fret over running out of juice while watching movies on a tablet. With up to six hours of battery life on a single charge, the ZenPad lets you watch two to three movies, or about half the season of House of Cards at one go - if you\'re into binge-watching.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image style=\"vc_box_shadow_circle\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" image=\"526\" css_animation=\"appear\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\n\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"527\" style=\"vc_box_shadow_circle_2\" border_color=\"grey\" img_link_large=\"yes\" img_link_target=\"_self\" css_animation=\"appear\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"\"]I am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lore