	(649,7,'2015-10-20 02:23:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00','[vc_row full_width=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_image=\"\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]When Eujin leaves home, he doesn\'t want to leave performance behind. With ASUSZenPad, he doesn\'t have to.\r\n\r\nGaming and movies make Eujin tick. From the classics of foreign cinema to the latest in co-op first person shooters, Eujin\'s pursuits demand performance. Watching a movie without full visual and audio detail won\'t cut it. Neither will lag, artifacts, or ghosting while gaming. So Eujin chooses ASUSZenPad. ZenPad delivers luxury on your terms, and for Eujin that means incredible movie and gaming performance on the go.\r\n\r\nZenPad offers up to 64-bit Intel processing and a full 4GB of RAM in an incredible 6.6 mm thin form factor. Paired with an available PowerVR 6430 GPU, that\'s plenty of computing horsepower for high definition movies and high performance gaming at home and on the go. Eujin likes his 8\" touchscreen in full 2K HD resolution so no detail is lost, no matter what he\'s watching or who he\'s fragging. Corning Gorilla Glass 3 glass with Native Damage Resistance (NDR) keeps that beautiful display safe from scratches and drops that would shatter lesser screens.\r\n\r\nEujin appreciates the beauty and flexibility of his ZenPad. Performance-wise, it\'s like having a desktop computer that fits in the palm of his hand. But the portability of this Android tablet means Eujin can watch and play where no desktop could ever go. At home, Eujin connects ZenPad to his living room theater system via HDMI (using a USB-C adapter) or wireless Miracast  the tablet serves up full HD video with surround sound, and powers big-screen gaming. From franchise favorites like Modern Combat 5 to new classics like Monument Valley, a ZenPad paired with a Bluetooth game controller makes a killer rig for casual and hardcore gaming alike.\r\n\r\nThen, when it\'s time to move to the bedroom or even head out the door, Eujin can pick up his ZenPad without missing a beat. ZenPad\'s VisualMaster technologies bring clear, vibrant moving images to life, whether they\'re streamed from online services or played back from up to 64GB of integrated local storage. Features like Intelligent Contrast, Sharpness Optimization, and Tru2Life+ adapt and enhance digital video for ultimate playback performance. Motion blur during fast action is a thing of the past, too, whether Eujin is enjoying an action movie or making his own action in Geometry Wars 3: Dimensions.\r\n\r\nGoing mobile doesn\'t mean sacrificing sound, either. DTS-HD Premium Sound and SonicMaster technology power awesome audio, whether Eujin is listening through headphones or ZenPad\'s dual front speakers. Compared to traditional tablets with side or rear mounted speakers, ZenPad\'s front stereo drivers produce three times the sound without sacrificing any clarity or detail. ASUS\' Golden Ear team tuned the tablet\'s audio for crystal-clear performance through speakers or headphones, and the integrated AudioWizard feature automatically tunes the audio profile for movies, gaming, music, and more, to match Eujin\'s mood. ZenPad is also the world\'s first tablet with DTS-HD Premium Sound, which converts stereo audio into virtual surround sound for a truly immersive experience.\r\n\r\nFor even higher quality audio on the go, Eujin snaps on his ZenPad Audio Cover. The world\'s first attached 5.1-channel surround sound accessory, the optional Audio Cover packs a full array of speakers into a foldable cover that doubles as a tablet stand. Featuring four sattelite speakers, a center channel driver, and a subwoofer, Audio Cover is a hit when Eujin and his friends gather for an impromptu movie watching session. No matter how many of them gather, or where they are, Audio Cover delivers the cinematic sound to match ZenPad\'s full HD display so everybody can get lost in the action.\r\n\r\nAt home and on the go, ZenPad delivers the performance Eujin demands from his movie and gaming gear. With incredible audio and visual performance, sleek style, and amazing accessories that bring full surround sound anywhere, ZenPad truly delivers luxury on your Eujin\'s terms - and yours.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','Incredible Movie and Gaming Performance on the Go','','draft','open','open','','','','','2015-10-20 02:23:23','2015-10-20 02:23:23','',0,'http://asus-zenpad.stagingapps.net/?p=649',0,'post','',0);
